<h3 class="h4 m3">Video playlists about Mental health</h3>
<div class='row row-skinny row-sm-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>All kinds of minds</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/9/all_kinds_of_minds'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/all_kinds_of_minds.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
9 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 12m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>These powerful stories shatter preconceived notions about mental illness, and pose the provocative question: What can the world learn from different kinds of minds? </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>The struggle of mental health</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/175/the_struggle_of_mental_health'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/struggle_of_mental_health.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
7 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 50m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Depression, schizophrenia, suicidal feelings—too often, these experiences stay private. These speakers who’ve struggled with mental illness boldly share their stories, in hopes that others don’t feel so alone.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Overcoming depression</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/287/4_ted_talks_on_overcoming_depr'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/overcoming_depression.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
4 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>1h 11m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Depression is an illness that many suffer alone. These speakers bravely share their own stories -- and how they recovered.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>Let's end the silence around suicide</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/296/let_s_end_the_silence_around_s'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/help_prevent_suicide.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
4 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>58:48</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>It's easy to suffer in silence, not knowing what to say to whom. These brave, honest talks suggest ways to open up, talk about it and seek help — as well as ways to offer it.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
